Callback Hell Di Javascript Bikin Serem Dibacanya

=====================================================

contoh code serhana :

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Ubah Warna Body Otomatis</title>
    <style>
      body {
        transition: background-color 0.5s ease;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Warna latar belakang akan berubah setiap 3 detik</h1>

    <script>
      function changeBodyColor() {
        const randomColor =
          "#" + Math.floor(Math.random() * 16777215).toString(16);
        document.body.style.backgroundColor = randomColor;
        console.log("Warna latar belakang diubah menjadi:", randomColor);
      }

      // Mengubah warna latar belakang setiap 3 detik
      setInterval(changeBodyColor, 3000);
    </script>
  </body>
</html>


=========================================================
